%20and%20prioritize%20planes%20more%20easily.%20LaGuardia%20was%20the%20example%20loop%20on%20the%20screens.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20ADB%20Safegate%20technology%20will%20be%20a%20parking%20aid%20that%20allows%20an%20aircraft%20to%20dock%20at%20a%20gate%20in%20virtually%20any%20weather%20condition.%20Zahir%20said%20this%20would%20be%20particularly%20useful%20during%20lightning%20storms%20when%20wing%20walkers%20are%20evacuated%20from%20the%20tarmac%20and%20forced%20to%20leave%20fully%20loaded%20planes%20sitting%20idle%20just%20meters%20from%20the%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZahir%20said%20the%20docking%20system%2C%20which%20can%20handle%20everything%20up%20to%20the%20mammoth%20Airbus%20A380%2C%20is%20already%20proving%20its%20efficiency%20at%20existing%20JFK%20terminals%20and%20at%20several%20other%20airports%20like%20LaGuardia%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222319%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dock%20aid%20demonstrating%20a%20regional%20jet%20parking%20at%20a%20gate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671bc51101ea6d83dee42040%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dock%20aid%20demonstrates%20how%20a%20regional%20jet%20would%20park%20at%20a%20gate.%20Zahir%20said%20the%20technology%20identifies%20each%20plane%20by%20its%20engines.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EComplementing%20the%20gate%20and%20ramp%20tower%20tech%20is%20ADB%20Safegate's%20AI-powered%20apron%20manager%20that%20can%20predict%20aircraft%20on-time%20performance%20and%20improve%20aircraft%20turn%20times%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20passengers%20can%20get%20on%20their%20way%20faster%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20identified%2025-30%20activities%20that%20every%20flight%20must%20go%20through%20from%20arrival%20to%20departure%2C%26quot%3B%20Zahir%20said