C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22helium%2010%20shock%20absorber%20data%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671820e601ea6d83dee34d9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Helium%2010%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BTennis%20grip%20tape%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22helium%2010%20grip%20tape%20data%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718211201ea6d83dee34d9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Helium%2010%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPickleball%20paddles%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22helium%2010%20data%20pickleball%20paddles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718213b9b3250dbbce94ebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Helium%2010%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPickleball%20paddles%20were%20the%20most%20intriguing%2C%20at%20least%20based%20on%20search%20volume%20and%20BSR%2C%20but%20with%20an%20average%20price%20of%20%2463%2C%20we%20wondered%20if%20they'd%20be%20too%20expensive%20to%20make%20on%20a%20%2410%2C000%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sent%20our%20list%20of%20racket-sports%20products%20and%20accompanying%20Helium%2010%20data%20to%20Reeves%20and%20Walter%20ahead%20of%20our%20call%2C%20not%20entirely%20sure%20what%20to%20make%20of%20the%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20entirely%20sure%20we%20were%20even%20using%20the%20software%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20met%20over%20Zoom%2C%20Reeves%20helped%20us%20nix%20a%20few%20products%20right%20off%20the%20bat.%20Tennis%20ball%20tubes%2C%