-sisters-death-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhen%20someone%20you%20love%20dies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20always%20abrupt%20and%20feels%20too%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wave%20goodbye%20at%20this%20beautiful%20triumphant%20moment%20and%20then%20it's%20just%20emptiness.%20It%20would%20feel%20like%2C%20you%20got%20to%20be%20kidding%20me%2C%20right%3F%20She's%20coming%20back%2C%20of%20course%2C%20which%20is%20what%20you%20feel%20when%20somebody%20goes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20points%20to%20the%20dog%20that%20appears%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20final%20scene%20of%20the%20film%20as%20a%20subtle%20clue%20that%20Almut%20has%20died%2C%20calling%20back%20to%20earlier%20in%20the%20film%20when%20Almut%20half-jokingly%20suggests%20getting%20an%20older%20dog%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-camp-grief-kids-whove-lost-parent-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20their%20daughter%20cope%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20death%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20egg-cracking%20moment%20is%20another%20motif%20brought%20back%20in%20the%20ending.%20That%20happens%20three%20times%20throughout%20the%20film%3A%20in%20the%20opening%20scene%2C%20when%20we're%20first%20introduced%20to%20Almut%2C%20then%20early%20in%20Tobias%20and%20Almut's%20relationship%20when%20she%20explains%20to%20him%20her%20method%20for%20egg-cracking%20(always%20on%20a%20flat%20surface%20and%20into%20a%20smaller%20bowl%20before%20it's%20transferred%20to%20a%20larger%20bowl)%2C%20and%20then%20in%20the%20final%20scene%20where%20Tobias%20and%20their%20daughter%20are%20using%20Almut's%20egg-cracking%20method%20after%20she%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20quick%20moment%20that%20takes%20on%20greater%20import%3A%20a%20simple%2C%20profound%20way%20of%20showing%20how%20Almut%20lives%20on%20for%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrowley%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20a%20risk%20to%20wrap%20up%20the%20film%20wit