%20Electoral%20Officer%20Neha%20Arora%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Jharkhand%20Minister%20Irfan%20Ansari%20for%20allegedly%20making%20derogatory%20remarks%20about%20BJP%20leader%20Sita%20Soren%20in%20Jamtara%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20in%20Jamtara%20district%20for%20violating%20MCC%20(model%20code%20of%20conduct)%20provisions.%20A%20strict%20advisory%20has%20also%20been%20issued%20to%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20Neha%20Arora%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Annapurna%20Devi%20said%20the%20statement%20made%20by%20Irfan%20Ansari%20exposes%20the%20mentality%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Irfan%20Ansari)%20has%20given%20a%20very%20wrong%20statement%20on%20Sita%20Soren.%20This%20exposes%20the%20mentality%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20Congress%20party%20is%20anti-women%20and%20anti-youth...I%20condemn%20this%20statement...Will%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20take%20back%20the%20tickets%20given%20to%20people%20with%20such%20a%20low%20level%20of%20thinking%3F%20The%20Congress%20party%20should%20remove%20such%20people%20from%20the%20cabinet%2C%26quot%3B%20Annapurna%20Devi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESita%20Soren%20said%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20understand%20how%20people%20like%20Mr%20Ansari%20get%20the%20courage%20to%20make%20such%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20unable%20to%20understand%20where%20he%20gets%20the%20courage%20to%20make%20such%20statements.%20Who%20is%20giving%20him%20the%20courage%20to%20make%20such%20statements%2C%20because%20no%20one%20has%20ever%20made%20such%20statements%20against%20me%20in%20Jharkhand...The%20party%20has%20informed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20about%20his%20statement.%20We%20will%20not%20forgive%20him...The%20entire%20tribal%20population%20is%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Ragini%20Singh%2C%20said%20insulting%20women%20is%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20his%20mentality.%20It%20is%20the%20policy%20of%20Congress%20to%20comment%20on%20a%20woman%20but%20BJP%20policy%20is%20to%20respect%20all%20the%20women%20whether%20they%20are%20from%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20Ansari%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20the%20Jamtara%20constituency%2C%20stirred%20controversy%20with%20his%20remarks%20about%20Sita%20Soren%2C%20his%20opponent%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Sita%20Soren%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20referred%20to%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Brejected%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bborrowed%20player%26quot%3B%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20journalist's%20question%20about%20competing%20against%20her%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20also%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Mr%20Ansari%20for%20using%20%26quot%3Bindecent%20language%26quot%3B%20against%20her%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20public%20would%20respond%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20%40INCIndia%20candidate%20Irfan%20Ansari%20must%20apologise%20for%20the%20indecent%20language%20he%20used%20against%20me%20in%20front%20of%20the%20media%20immediately%20after%20filing%20his%20nomination.%20He%20has%20previously%20made%20personal%20comments%20about%20me%2C%20but%20this%20time%20he%20has%20crossed%20all%20limits.%20Irfan%20ji%20%40IrfanAnsariMLA%2C%20apologise%2C%20or%20be%20prepared%20for%20fierce%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indecent%20words%20you%20used%20while%20holding%20such%20a%20respected%20position%20have%20alarmed%20women%20across%20society.%20If%20you%20can%20use%20such%20words%20for%20me%2C%20what%20must%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20women%20face%3F%20As%20lo