ionate%20reaction%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Israeli%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20for%20it.%20We%20are%20completely%20coordinating%20with%20our%20allies%2C%20especially%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20is%20completely%20backing%20our%20moves.%20It%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20Israel%20could%20have%20done%20much%20more%20to%20inflict%20damage%20on%20Iran%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20limit%20its%20response%20out%20of%20responsibility%20because%20we%20want%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20this%20operation%20that%20the%20Israeli%20cabinet%20has%20determined%20-%20to%20completely%20eradicate%20the%20military%20capabilities%20of%20Hamas%2C%20to%20bring%20back%20our%20hostages%20and%20make%20sure%20Hamas%20doesn't%20rearm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20north%2C%20where%20Israel%20shares%20a%20border%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20ambassador%20said%20that%20the%20objective%20is%20to%20resettle%20Israeli%20communities%20in%20the%20areas%20from%20which%20they%20were%20evacuated%20because%20of%20attacks%20from%20Hezbollah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20operating%20there%20as%20well%2C%20we%20have%20uprooted%20the%20military%20infrastructure%20that%20Hezbollah%20has%20created%20there%20for%20decades.%20And%20we%20will%20not%20agree%20that%20Iran%20will%20try%20to%20intervene%20in%20that%20and%20attack%20Israel.%20If%20they%20continue%20doing%20that%2C%20Israel%20will%20feel%20free%20to%20act%20in%20a%20much%20more%20decisive%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Pay%20The%20Price'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Israel%20is%20locked%20in%20a%20never-ending%20war%2C%20Mr%20Azar%20said%20while%20that%20may%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20his%20country%20is%20defending%20itself%20and%20has%20created%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20Hamas%20can%20no%20longer%20attack%20it%20with%20missiles%20and%20the%20leadership%20of%20Hezbollah%20ha