ham-pisses-off-miami-neighbors-they-are-not-private%2Famp_articleshow%2F114629880.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvictoria-and-david-beckham-pisses-off-miami-neighbors-they-are-not-private%2Famp_articleshow%2F114629880.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGST%20A%20Classical%20Example%20Of%20Cooperative%20Federalism%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIntroduction%20of%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20in%20India%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bclassical%20example%20of%20cooperative%20federalism%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20have%2C%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20evolved%20a%20robust%20framework%20on%20federalism%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20states'%20rights%20are%20protected%2C%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20on%20%60Understanding%20Federalism%20and%20Its%20Potential%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20inaugural%20annual%20lecture%20series%20organized%20by%20the%20Marathi%20daily%20%60Loksatta'.%20Federalism%2C%20for%20Indians%2C%20is%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonolithic%20concept%26quot%3B%20but%20has%20multiple%20facets%2C%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECooperative%20federalism%20is%20a%20system%20of%20governance%20where%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20work%20together%20to%20%26quot%3Biron%20out%20differences%20to%20achieve%20the%20common%20goal%20of%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dialogue%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states%20must%20be%20placed%20on%20%26quot%3Btwo%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%26quot%3B%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20at%20one%20end%20are%20collaborative%20discussions%20that%20cooperative%20federalism%20fosters%2C%20while%20%26quot%3Binterstitial%20contestation%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20states%20and%20the%20Union%20are%20at%20the%20other%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20forms%20of%20dialogue%20are%20equally%20important%20for%20federalism%20and%20for%20our%20nation%20to%20flourish%2C%20and%20what%20better%20example%20(one%20can%20think%20of)%20than%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20GST%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%201990%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20economy%20underwent%20market%20reforms%2C%20the%20economy%20has%20come%20to%20occupy%20the%20centrestage%20of%20the%20political%20discourse%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amendment%20in%20the%20Constitution%20to%20reflect%20and%20embody%20the%20GST%2C%20is%20to%20my%20mind%20a%20classical%20example%20of%20collaborative%2C%20cooperative%20federalism%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courts%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20developing%20the%20principles%20of%20Indian%20federalism%2C%20said%20the%20chief%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20courts%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20development%2C%20bringing%20out%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20doctrine%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20states%20in%20terms%20of%20identity%20and%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20courts%20evolved%20a%20robust%20jurisprudential%20framework%20on%20federalism%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20state's%20rights%20are%20protected%2C%20identity%20of%20various%20communities%20is%20fostered%20and%20the%20value%20of%20representation%20is%20promoted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20nature%20of%20our%20Constitution%20has%20undergone%20a%20change%20by%20the%20actual%20operation%20of%20the%20democracy%2C%20Chef%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20of%20federalism%20that%20was%20envisaged%20by%20our%20founding%20fathers%20and%20mothers%20has%20not%20remained%20static%2C%20it's%20a%20concept%20which%20has%20evolved%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20evolution%2C%20the%20maturity%20and%20strength%20of%20our%20political%20system%20to%20incorporate%20more%20autonomy%20for%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Constitution%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btransformative%20document%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20CJI%20said%2C%20while%20also%20noting%20that%20issues%20like%20climate%20change%2C%20AI%2C%20data%20privacy%20and%20cyber%20crime%20transcend%20the%20territorial%20boundaries%20which%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20federal%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20new%20challenges%20ill-fit%20the%20conventional%20modes%20of%20union%20and%20state%20subjects.....some%20Indian%20states%20are%20severely%20impacted%20by%20the%20perils%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20while%20some%20may%20be%20more%20prone%20to%20cyber%20attacks%20due%20to%20the%20greater%20volume%20of%20virtual%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20federalism%20in%20the%20years%20gone%20by%20was%20adjusting%20to%20the%20political%20realities%20of%20the%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20legislative%20powers%2C%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%20it%20should%20also%20be%20evaluated%20based%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20foster%20democracy%20and%20constitutional%20ideals%20of%20equality%2C%20liberty%2C%20dignity%20and%20fraternity%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729960260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fi33m3aro_chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-_625x300_21_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgst-a-classical-example-of-collaborative-cooperative-federalism-chief-justice-6880423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Introduction%20of%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20