hewan%2C%20Canada%2C%20is%20facing%20an%20unforeseen%20problem%3A%20there%20are%20no%20contenders%20for%20the%20mayorship%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ECKOM.COM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20current%20Mayor%20George%20Williams%2C%20who%20assumed%20office%20in%20November%202021%2C%20is%20scheduled%20to%20resign%2C%20leaving%20his%20position%20unfilled%20and%20without%20any%20candidates.%20Furthermore%2C%20there%20are%20still%20no%20nominees%20for%20a%20Town%20Council%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20rounds%20of%20candidate%20applications%20have%20been%20released%20to%20promote%20mayor%20nominations%2C%20but%20thus%20far%2C%20no%20one%20has%20shown%20interest%2C%20according%20to%20Chief%20Administrative%20Officer%20Amber%20Dashney.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20concerning%2C%20but%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20someone%20will%20step%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Dashney%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ckom.com%2F2024%2F10%2F24%2Fits-not-unusual-town-of-kyle-looking-for-mayor-candidate%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECKOM.COM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20will%20designate%20a%20deputy%20mayor%20to%20assume%20the%20duties%20of%20mayor%20if%20the%20post%20is%20not%20filled%20by%20the%20election%20on%20November%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20meeting%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20a%20date%20for%20a%20by-election%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20calling%20a%20by-election%20until%20we%20fill%20the%20mayor%20spot%20and%20the%20other%20councilor%20spot%2C%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Dashney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGordon%20Barnhart%2C%20former%20President%20of%20the%20Saskatchewan%20Urban%20Municipalities%20Association%20(SUMA)%2C%20said%20it%20can%20occur%20from%20time%20to%20time%20were%20nobody%20steps%20forward%20for%20council%20or%20mayoral%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20that%20it's%20common%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20unusual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20for%20small%20communities%20to%20find%20enough%20people%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20run%20for%20mayor%20or%20for%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Barnhart%20was%20elected%20as%20a%20councillor%20for%20the%20Town%20of%20Saltcoats%20-%20a%20community%2030%20kilometres%20southeast%20of%20Yorkton%20-%20through%20a%20byelection%20after%20some%20convincing%20from%20local%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20several%20vacant%20councillor%20positions%2C%20Barnhart%20said%20the%20town%20risked%20not%20meeting%20quorum%20at%20council%20meetings.%20He%20would%20go%20on%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20councillor%20in%20Saltcoats%20until%202020%2C%20before%20being%20elected%20as%20mayor%20where%20he%20sat%20until%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20really%20a%20dedication%20to%20your%20community%20where%20you%20feel%20that%20you%20can%20make%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnhart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww12.statcan.gc.ca%2Fcensus-recensement%2F2021%2Fdp-pd%2Fprof%2Findex.cfm%3FLang%3DE%5C%22%3E2021%20Statistics%20Canada%20census%20data%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Town%20of%20Kyle%20has%20population%20of%20413%2C%20and%20the%20Town%20of%20Saltcoats%20has%20a%20population%20of%20473.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20towns%20and%20villages%20have%20smaller%20populations%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20Barnhart%20said%20people's%20time%20and%20confidence%20may%20be%20factors%20that%20prevent%20people%20from%20running%20for%20a%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20SUMA%20said%20as%20long%20as%20council%20can%20maintain%20quorum%2C%20it%20can%20continue%20with%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it's%20rare%2C%20it's%20not%20unheard%20of%20for%20no%20one%20to%20put%20their%20name%20forward%20for%20mayor%2C%20or%20for%20too%20few%20people%20to%20put%20their%20names%20forward%20for%20council%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20