20Reddy%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20love%20and%20affection%26quot%3B%20would%20transfer%20his%20and%20his%20wife's%20shares%20of%20Saraswati%20Power%20and%20Industries%20through%20gift%20deed%20to%20his%20sister%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20outcome%20of%20pending%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jagan%20Reddy%20conveying%20his%20intention%20to%20revoke%20the%20MoU%2C%20in%20September%20moved%20NCLT%20(National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal)%20accusing%20Sharmila%20of%20illegally%20transferring%20shares%20of%20the%20firm%20held%20by%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20Bharathi%2C%20in%20her%20and%20mother%20Vijayamma's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJaganmohan%20Reddy%20says%20this%20happens%20in%20every%20household%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20'%3Cem%3Eghar%20ghar%20ki%20kahani%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20What%20is%20%3Cem%3Eghar%20ghar%20ki%20kahani%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20Is%20dragging%20a%20mother%20to%20court%20a%20ghar%20ghar%20ki%20kahani%3F%20Is%20it%20an%20issue%20that%20happens%20in%20every%20household%3F%20Don't%20you%20have%20humanity%3F%20Don't%20you%20have%20any%20sentiments%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Sharmila%20asked%20with%20tearful%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20despite%20holding%20the%20MoU%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20she%20never%20tried%20to%20approach%20any%20court%20(for%20the%20settlement)%20or%20any%20media%20house%20for%20(publicity)%20fearing%20it%20would%20tarnish%20the%20reputation%20of%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20YSRCP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20her%20uncle%20YV%20Subba%20Reddy%20that%20the%20companies%20in%20question%20are%20owned%20by%20Jagan%20Reddy%2C%20Ms%20Sharmila%20termed%20it%20as%20false%20and%20said%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20swear%20on%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sharmila%20also%20dared%20Jagan%20and%20Subba%20Reddy%20to%20swear%20on%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20clinched%20a%20huge%20victory%20in%20