gendra%20Pawar%2C%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20is%20set%20to%20contest%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%20against%20his%20uncle%20Ajit%20Pawar%20from%20Baramati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYugendra%20Pawar%20is%20the%20grandnephew%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20will%20be%20making%20his%20political%20debut%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20him%20contesting%20election%20against%20his%20own%20uncle%20who%20has%20won%20this%20seat%20seven%20times%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20it%20is%20quite%20sad%2C%20quite%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20had%20to%20come%20in%20the%20family.%20Not%20in%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20but%20it%20started%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20we%20were%20always%20together%20and%20even%20the%20incumbent%20MLA%20was%20always%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20party%20and%20family%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%20Sahab.%20What%20happened%20all%20of%20India%20has%20seen.%20The%20party%20split%20and%20the%20symbol%20was%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20election%20commission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%20will%20see%20another%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20contest%2C%20after%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20daughter%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20defeated%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20wife%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20split%20the%20NCP%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYugendra%20Pawar%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20unfortunate%20but%20all%20of%20us%20in%20the%20family%20decided%20that%20we%20need%20to%20stay%20with%20Pawar%20Sahab%20because%20he%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20he%20is%20the%20patriarch%20of%20the%20family%20and%20it%20is%20because%20of%20him%20that%20not%20only%20Baramati%20but%20everybody%20around%20also%20prospered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYugendra%20Pawar%20feels%20that%20the%20fight%20against%20his%20own%20uncle%20won't%20be%20tough%20but%20won't%20be%20easy%20either.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it%20will%20be%20tough%20but%20I%20don't%20even%20think%20that%20it%20will%20be%20easy%20either.%20Initially%2C%20Pawar%20Sahab%20was%20supporting%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20we%20fondly%20call%20him%20Dada%2C%20but%20people%20of%20Baramati%20in%20large%20numbers%20are%20behind%20Pawar%20Sahab%20and%20that%20is%20what%20they%20showed%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20They%20will%20show%20this%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20as%20well%20as%20other%20elections%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20political%20debut%20from%20Baramati%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20satisfying%2C%20I%20am%20quite%20happy%20and%20I%20humbly%20accept%20the%20responsibility%20given%20to%20me%20by%20the%20party%20and%20respectable%20Pawar%20Sahab%2C%20State%20President%20Jayant%20Patil%20and%20as%20well%20as%20our%20Working%20President%20Supriya%20Tai%20Sule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20list%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20party%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20faction)%20has%20fielded%2012%20sitting%20MLAs%20who%20remained%20loyal%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar%20when%20the%20party%20split%20last%20year.%20The%20party%20declared%20its%20first%20list%20of%2045%20candidates%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20has%20been%20allotted%2085%20seats%20in%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20among%20the%20three%20parties%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baramati%20candidate%20emphasised%20various%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lot%20of%20issues%2C%20there%20are%20a%20range%20of%20problems%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20Like%20crime%20has%20increased%20not%20only%20in%20Baramati%20but%20all%20of%20Maharashtra.%20Then%20there%20is%20also%20a%20local%20issue%20like%20the%20old%20people%2C%20we%20call%20them%20Gao%20Pudharis%2C%20these%20local%20netas%20or%20the%20sewaks%20have%20not%20been%20changed%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20They%20have%20not%20been%20the%20way%20a%20lok%20pratinidhi%20should%20behave.%20That%20needs%20to%20change%20somewhere.%20We%20need%20someone%20who%20will%20be%20amongst%20them%2C%20somebody%20who%20will%20be%20with%20them%2C%20will%20be%20available%2C%20who%20can%20hear%20them%20out%20and%20that%20system%20has%20not%20only%20been%20there%20in%20Baramati%20for%20quite%20a%20long%20time%20that%20needs%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Yugendra%20Pawar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnemployment%20is%20a%20very%20big%20issue%20in%20Baramati%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Also%2C%20water%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20Baramati.%20Today%2C%20even%20though%20the%20monsoon%20is%20going%20on%2C%20there%20are%20close%20to%2025%20to%2030%20villages%20that%20still%20do%20not%20have%20drinking%20water.%20This%20is%20a%20drought-prone%20area.%20Pawar%20sahab%20brought%20water%20to%20the%20region%20around%2035%20to%2040%20years%20ago%20but%20after%20that%20not%20a%20single%20irrigation%20scheme%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20Baramati%20because%20of%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20villages%20today%20also%20are%20still%20drought-prone.%20We%20have%20a%20river%20over%20here%20called%20the%20Nira%2C%20the%20water%20is%20so%20polluted%20that%20even%20though%20we%20have%20water%20we%20cannot%20spread%20it%20to%20where%20it%20is%20actually%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20controversies%20going%20around%20the%20reservation%20system%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReservation%20is%20something%20that%20was%20given%20to%20us%20by%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20there%20are%20certain%20sections%20of%20society%20that%20still%20do%20need%20them.%20It%20will%20still%20be%20useful%20to%20them%20and%20our%20MP%20from%20Baramati%20Supriya%20Tai%20Sule%20has%20also%20spoken%20on%20this%20issue%20in%20Parliament%20and%20asked%20for%20reservation%20for%20certain%20sections%20so%20I%20personally%20also%20support%20her%20stand%20and%20our%20party's%20stand%20on%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYugendra%20Pawar%20has%20been%20to%20all%20the%20villages%20in%20Baramati%20before%20contesting%20the%20election%20and%20plans%20to%20go%20around%20the%20area%20again%20after%20two%20days.%20%26quot%3BPawar%20sahab%20is%20my%20mentor%2C%20my%20guide%20or%20%3Cem%3E'margdarshak'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20always%20tells%20me%20that%20you%20should%20go%20amongst%20people%2C%20you%20should%20not%20only%20focus%20on%20big%20cities%20or%20the%20big%20villages%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20go%20to%20small%20%3Cem%3E'wadis'%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3E'vastis'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20I%20go%20there%20people%2C%20tell%20me%20after%20Pawar%20Sahab%20nobody%20else%20has%20ever%20reached%20out%20to%20them.%20Being%20there%2C%20you%20get%20to%20see%20the%20constituency%20and%20the%20issues%2C%20the%20problems%20that%20people%20are%20facing.%20I%20like%20to%20be%20on%20the%20field%20and%20not%20sitting%20on%20a%20desk%20or%20(in%20front%20of%20a)%20computer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729959240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Flrogfps4_ajit-pawar-sharad-pawar-pti-_625x300_26_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyugendra-pawar-ajit-pawar-maharashtra-elections-baramati-unfortunate-sharad-pawars-grandnephew-on-contesting-against-ajit-pawar-6879807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20familial%20ties%2C%20Yugendra%20Pawar%2C%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%2C%20is%20set%20to%20contest%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%2