%2F114625482.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114625482.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan%20shared%20his%20emotional%20turmoil%20over%20a%20fallout%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20describing%20their%20bond%20as%20brotherly.%20Despite%20their%20rift%20occurring%20at%20Katrina%20Kaif's%202008%20birthday%20party%2C%20the%20duo%20reconciled%20in%202013%2C%20inspiring%20fans.%20Currently%2C%20both%20stars%20are%20focusing%20on%20their%20respective%20film%20ventures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-salman-khan-opened-up-about-his-brotherly-love-for-shah-rukh-khan-amid-their-2008-rift%2Farticleshow%2F114625482.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMilitary%20Worked%20In%20Unimaginable%20Conditions%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20China%20Pact%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20patrolling%20agreement%20with%20China%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20rebuild%20trust%20and%20for%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20each%20other%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interaction%20with%20students%20from%20a%20university%20in%20Pune%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20breakthrough%20with%20China%20was%20possible%20because%20the%20military%20enabled%20India%20to%20stand%20its%20ground%20and%20make%20its%20point%20and%20diplomacy%20also%20did%20its%20part.%20A%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20in%20border%20areas%2C%20which%20enabled%20effective%20deployment%20of%20the%20military%2C%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20patrolling%20and%20disengagement%20agreement%20in%20the%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20areas%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20and%20what%20can%20be%20expected%20from%20the%20future%20of%20India-China%20relations%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%202020%2C%20the%20situation%20at%20the%20border%20has%20been%20very%20disturbed%20and%20that%20has%2C%20understandably%2C%20had%20a%20very%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20overall%20relationship.%20Since%20September%202020%2C%20we%20have%20been%20negotiating%20with%20the%20Chinese%20on%20how%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20there%20were%20different%20aspects%20to%20the%20solution%20but%20the%20pressing%20one%20was%20disengagement%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20troops%20are%20very%20very%20close%20up%20to%20each%20other%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20something%20happening%2C%20god%20forbid%2C%20is%20there%26quot%3B.%20The%20other%20aspects%2C%20he%20said%20are%20de-escalation%2C%20given%20the%20troop%20buildup%20by%20China%20and%20India's%20response%20to%20it%2C%20and%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20boundary%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%2C%20for%20now%2C%20is%20disengagement%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20while%20there%20had%20been%20understandings%20in%20some%20areas%20after%202020%2C%20blocking%20of%20patrolling%20remained%20an%20issue%20which%20was%20being%20negotiated%20for%20two%20years.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20what%20happened%20on%20October%2021%20was%20that%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20we%20came%20to%20the%20understanding%20that%20patrolling%20would%20be%20resumed%20how%20it%20used%20to%20be%20before...%20This%20was%20important%20because%20it%20was%20an%20affirmation%20that%20if%20we%20can%20do%20the%20disengagement%2C%20then%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20the%20leadership%20level%20to%20meet%2C%20which%20is%20what%20happened%20(with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20meeting)%20in%20Russia's%20Kazan%20during%20the%20BRICS%20summit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20interaction%20at%20FLAME%20University%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFuture%20Of%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20where%20the%20India-China%20relationship%20goes%20from%20here%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20early.%20We%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20things%20to%20settle%20themselves.%20Because%2C%20after%20four%20years%20of%20a%20very%20disturbed%20border%20where%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20have%20been%20shattered%2C%20it%20will%20naturally%20take%20time%20to%20rebuild%20a%20degree%20of%20trust%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20work%20with%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20reached%20where%20we%20have%20today%2C%20there%20are%20two%20reasons%20for%20it.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20very%20determined%20effort%20on%20our%20part%20to%20stand%20our%20ground%20and%20make%20our%20point%20and%20this%20would%20only%20happen%20because%20the%20military%20was%20there%20in%20very%2C%20very%20unimaginable%20conditions%20to%20defend%20the%20country.%20The%20military%20did%20its%20part%20and%20diplomacy%20did%20its%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20was%20the%20importance%20given%20to%20improving%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20have%20put%20in%20almost%20five%20times%20annually%20the%20resources%20that%20would%20be%20there%20a%20decade%20ago.%20That's%20showing%20results%20and%20that%20enables%20the%20military%20to%20be%20effectively%20deployed.%20I%20would%20be%20patient.%20When%20PM%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20met%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20and%20national%20security%20advisers%20would%20meet%20and%20see%20how%20this%20should%20be%20taken%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20On%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20reported%20on%20Friday%20on%20satellite%20images%20showing%20tents%20and%20semi-permanent%20structures%20being%20removed%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20patrolling%20agreement%20had%20been%20announced%20by%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20on%20Monday%20and%20army%20sources%20had%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20process%20of%20disengagement%20would%20be%20completed%20in%20the%20two%20contentious%20areas%20by%20October%2029.%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Jinping%20welcomed%20the%20agreement%20when%20they%20met%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stand-off%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20armies%20began%20on%20May%202020%20and%20a%20deadly%20clash%20took%20place%20in%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20the%20next%20month%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20and%20an%20unspecified%20number%20on%20the%20Chinese%20side%20also%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20troop%20buildup%20followed%20and%2C%20after%20months%20of%20talks%2C%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20withdrew%20from%20the%20contentious%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20in%20Ladakh%20in%20September%202022%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20pre-April-2020%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729948800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fs43j36bc_s-jaishankar-brics-summit-pti_625x300_24_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-ties-depsang-demchok-disengagement-military-worked-in-unimaginable-conditions-s-jaishankar-on-china-pact-6879775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20patrolling%20agreement%20with%20China%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20rebuild%20trust%20and%20for%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20each%20other%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-ties-depsang-demchok-disengagement-military-worked-in-unimaginable-conditions-s-jaishankar-on-china-pact-6879775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCertain%20Individuals...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Makes%20Intentions%20Clear%20After%20India's%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0India%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20won't%20%26quot%3Boverreact%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20embarrassing%20series%20defeat%20against%20New%20Zealand%20but%20he%20underlined%20the%20necessity%20to%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20chat%20with%20certain%20individuals%26quot%3B%20to%20discuss%20the%20way%20forward.%20India%20lost%20the%20second%20Test%20by%20113%20runs%20after%20failing%20in%20pursuit%20of%20a%20stiff%20359-run%20target.%20This%20was%20India's%20first%20home%20series%20defeat%20in%2012%20years%20after%20conceding%20a%20four-match%20rubber%20against%20England%201-2%20in%202012-13.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interim%2C%20India%20won%2018%20series%20at%20home%20on%20the%20trot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20overreact.%20But%20you%20need%20to%20have%20a%20quiet%20chat%20with%20certain%20individuals%20and%20let%20them%20know%20where%20they%20are%20at%20and%20what%2C%20as%20a%20team%2C%20we%20require%20from%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriving%20home%20the%20reality%20might%20be%20on%20top%20of%20his%20agenda%20now%2C%20but%20Rohit%20did%20not%20want%20to%20make%20a%20spectacle%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20need%20to%20make%20them%20sit%20in%20a%20team%20room%20on%20a%20one-on-one%20basis%20and%20go%20through%20their%20innings%20and%20tell%20them%20this%20is%20what%20you%20should%20be%20doing.%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20is%20the%20right%20forum%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20we%20have%20lost%20a%20series%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20anything%20that%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20differently%20or%20do%20differently.%20But%20yeah%2C%20we%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20come%20out%20of%20those%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20he%20trusts%20his%20teammates%2C%20who%20have%20won%20India%20so%20many%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20doubt%20anyone's%20ability.%20I%20won't%20do%20much%20postmortem%20of%20this%2C%20but%20batters%20must%20come%20with%20their%20plans%20and%20trust%20on%20the%20plans%20like%20New%20Zealand%20batters%20showed.%26quot%3B%20Some%20of%20the%20seniors%20in%20the%20side%20such%20as%20batting%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20senior%20spinners%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20quite%20peripheral%20in%20their%20impact%20on%20this%20series%2C%20which%20India%20lost%200-2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seasoned%20triumvirate%20apart%2C%20even%20skipper%20Rohit%20could%20not%20fire%20in%20the%20ongoing%20series%20as%20his%20last%20four%20innings%20read%3A%202%2C%2052%2C%200%20and%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbaikar%20understands%20that%20such