ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fneed-to-chat-with-certain-individuals-rohit-sharma-makes-intentions-clear-after-indias-historic-loss-vs-nz-6879806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20vs%20New%20Zealand%3A%20Driving%20home%20the%20reality%20might%20be%20on%20top%20of%20his%20agenda%20now%2C%20but%20Rohit%20Sharma%20did%20not%20want%20to%20make%20a%20spectacle%20out%20of%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Big%20Caution%20To%20Social%20Media%20Platforms%20Over%20Fake%20Bomb%20Threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20spate%20of%20fake%20bomb%20threats%20issued%20to%20airlines%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20public%20order%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20told%20social%20media%20platforms%20while%20ordering%20them%20to%20act%20against%20the%20spread%20of%20such%20misinformation%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20warned%20the%20social%20media%20companies%20that%20the%20exemption%20available%20to%20them%20for%20third-party%20content%20as%20intermediaries%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20will%20not%20apply%20if%20they%20don't%20follow%20their%20due%20diligence%20obligations%20or%20aid%20in%20committing%20an%20unlawful%20act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20advisory%20sent%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20said%20air%20travellers%20and%20security%20agencies%20have%20been%20affected%20because%20of%20the%20hoax%20bomb%20threats%2C%20which%20have%20disrupted%20the%20normal%20operations%20of%20airlines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20hoax%20bomb%20threats%2C%20while%20affecting%20a%20large%20number%20of%20citizens%2C%20also%20destabilise%20the%20economic%20security%20of%20the%20country.%20Further%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20spread%20of%20such%20hoax%20bomb%20threats%20has%20been%20observed%20to%20be%20dangerously%20unrestrained%20due%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20option%20of%20'forwarding%2Fre-sharing%2F%20re-posting%2F%20re-tweeting'%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platforms.%20Such%20hoax%20bomb%20threats%20are%20mostly%20misinformation%20that%20is%20massively%20disrupting%20public%20order%2C%20operations%20of%20airlines%20and%20security%20of%20the%20airline%20travellers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20the%20advisory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20platforms%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20carry%20out%20due%20diligence%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20(IT%20Act)%2C%202000%2C%20and%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%20(IT%20Rules)%2C%202021%2C%20to%20remove%20misinformation%20that%20affects%20public%20order%20and%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20the%20platforms%20to%20stop%20the%20posting%20and%20sharing%20of%20such%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%20or%20false%26quot%3B%20information%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20exemption%20from%20liability%20for%20third-party%20information%2C%20data%2C%20or%20communication%20hosted%20by%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20will%20not%20apply%20%26quot%3Bif%20such%20intermediaries%20do%20not%20follow%20the%20due%20diligence%20obligations%20as%20prescribed%20under%20the%20IT%20Act%20read%20with%20IT%20Rules%2C%202021%20or%20abetted%20or%20aided%2C%20in%20the%20commission%20of%20the%20unlawful%20act%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20due%20diligence%20obligations%20were%20not%20followed%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20the%20platforms%20would%20be%20liable%20for%20action%20under%20the%20IT%20Act%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20has%20replaced%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20urged%20the%20companies%20to%20make%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20such%20threats%20from%20being%20disseminated%20on%20their%20platforms%20and%20remove%20such%20content%20or%20disable%20access%20to%20it.%20The%20government%20also%20remin