caption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPadmaja%20has%20created%20a%20space%20where%20luxury%20resides%20in%20the%20melodies%20of%20birdsong%20and%20the%20thrill%20of%20spotting%20a%20leopard%20in%20its%20natural%20habitat.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy.%20There%20were%20initial%20hiccups%20with%20funding%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20find%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20tourism%20industry%2C%20which%20often%20has%20set%20expectations%20of%20luxury.%20But%20Padmaja%20is%20a%20force%20of%20nature%20herself.%20Remembering%20the%20early%20days%20when%20a%20travel%20agent%20asked%20her%20why%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20any%20floodlights%2C%20attached%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20ACs%20blowing%20in%20every%20room%2C%20she%20responded%20by%20emphasising%20that%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20resort%20but%20a%20jungle%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20projects%20that%20employ%2099%25%20tribal%20workers%2C%20Padmaja%20ensures%20that%20local%20communities%20are%20not%20only%20engaged%20in%20but%20also%20benefit%20from%20conservation%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20penny%20goes%20to%20the%20tribal%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Women%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20become%20leaders%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20poaching.%20Whether%20it%20be%20exercising%20their%20right%20of%20civic%20arrest%20or%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20mining%20lobby%2C%20Padmaja%20describes%20how%20women%20rally%20together%20to%20protect%20their%20environment%2C%20offsetting%20the%20traditional%20gender%20dynamics%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan.%20By%20employing%20these%20women%20in%20the%20camp%2C%20teaching%20them%20self%20defence%2C%20and%20educating%20them%2C%20Bhagheera%E2%80%99s%20camp%20serves%20as%20a%20means%20of%20confidence%20building%20and%20economic%20empowerment.%20It%20provides%20women%20with%20the%20tools%20and%20knowledge%20to%20take%20on%20leadership%20roles%20in%20conservation%20and