C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EManisha%2C%20from%20Mahendragarh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20was%20in%20search%20of%20a%20good%20doctor%20after%20her%20baby%E2%80%99s%20birth.%20Living%20in%20a%20remote%20town%2C%20she%20explains%20that%20she%20would%20have%20to%20travel%20150%20km%20to%20see%20a%20qualified%20paediatrician.%20After%20discovering%20Babynama%20on%20Instagram%2C%20she%20joined%20their%20WhatsApp%20group%20when%20her%20baby%20was%20just%2013%20days%20old%20and%20has%20remained%20a%20user%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20qualified%20doctor%20nearby%2C%20and%20travelling%20for%20four%20hours%20is%20not%20practical%20with%20a%20newborn.%20But%20Babynama%20has%20been%20a%20lifesaver%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%20all%20my%20queries%20answered%20instantly%2C%20from%20breastfeeding%20and%20colic%20issues%20to%20finding%20the%20right%20baby%20products%20to%20prevent%20rashes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallika%2C%20a%20first-time%20mother%20from%20Indore%2C%20echoes%20Manisha%E2%80%99s%20sentiments.%20Although%20she%20has%20access%20to%20qualified%20doctors%2C%20she%20notes%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20ask%20every%20question%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20paediatrician%2C%20as%20time%20is%20often%20limited.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20Babynama%2C%20I%20can%20ask%20every%20single%20doubt%20and%20get%20an%20immediate%20answer.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20growth%20tracking%2C%20milestones%2C%20weight%20checks%2C%20or%20the%20right%20time%20and%20dosage%20for%20paracetamol%2C%20every%20concern%20is%20addressed.%20We%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20ask%20anything%2C%20which%20is%20great%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mallika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2F2-2