species.%20We%20work%20closely%20with%20local%20and%20indigenous%20communities%20to%20create%20sustainable%20livelihoods%20that%20benefit%20both%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20When%20we%20invest%20in%20conservation%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20investing%20in%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarynaturefoundation.org%2Farticle%2Fmeet-koustubh-sharma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanctuary%20Nature%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsnowleopard.org%2Fmeet-snow-leopard-trusts-new-conservation-science-director-dr-koustubh-sharma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShiv%20Kumar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%202019%20when%20Shiv%20Kumar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Deputy%20Range%20Officer%20at%20Lahaul%20forest%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20first%20spotted%20a%20snow%20leopard.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274641%2Fforest-guard-officer-photographs-snow-leopard-conservation-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20he%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunforgettable%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20Thereafter%2C%20Shiv%20began%20conservation%20awareness%20classes%20about%20snow%20leopards%20among%20school%20children%20for%20the%20animal%E2%80%99s%20protection.%20He%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20villagers%20to%20inform%20them%20about%20its%20importance%2C%20threatened%20existence%20and%20its%20need%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20livestock%20belonging%20to%20the%20Gaddi%20community%20%E2%80%94%20a%20community%20of%20migratory%20shepherds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20locals%20in%20the%20Lahaul%20area%20remai