Cp%3EAnd%20today%2C%20the%20menu%20at%20Bungalow%20in%20East%20Village%2C%20New%20York%2C%20reflects%20these%20sensibilities.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20culinary%20virtuoso%20has%20reiterated%20how%20his%20latest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20last%20%E2%80%94%20gastronomic%20endeavour%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20crafts%20they%20have%20perfected%20over%20generations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hail%20from%20a%20small%20town%2C%20a%20small%20community%20where%20street%20food%20was%20the%20only%20way.%20In%20my%20growing%20up%20years%2C%20there%20was%20just%20one%20restaurant%20in%20Amritsar.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20food%20of%20street%20vendors%20that%20made%20us%20go%20%E2%80%98wow%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20from%20the%20English%20word%20for%20%3Cem%3Ebangla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(single-story%20home)%2C%20coined%20during%20India%E2%80%99s%20colonial%20past%2C%20Bungalow%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307799%2Flondon-oldest-indian-restaurant-veeraswamy-history-nehru-gandhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvitation%20to%20experience%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20exceptional%20cuisine.%20With%20a%20menu%20featuring%20a%20repository%20of%20time-honoured%20recipes%20documented%20from%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%2028%20states%20in%20all%20its%20diversity%20and%20hues%2C%20the%20space%20invites%20you%20to%20reimagine%20classics%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBungalow%3A%20A%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99%20for%20Indian%20immigrants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20a%20reservation%20at%20this%20grand%20establishment%20is%20no%20easy%20feat%2C%20more%20so%20once%20the%20festive%20season%20in%20India%20sets%20in%20(October%20to%20December).%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20habit%20of%20going%20to%20lengths%20to%20recreate%20the%20Diwali%20magic%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20foodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProof%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20my%20conversation%20with%20him.%20Stumped%20while%20trying%20to%20procure%20%3Cem%3Eparijaat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eflowers%20(a%20common%20feature%20in%20Indian%20homes%20during%20Diwali)%2C%20he%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20a%20guest%2C%20observing%20his%20frenzy%2C%20made%20him%20his%20very%20own%20bunch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eparijaat%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20from%20crochet!%20The%20flowers%20now%20occupy%20centre%20stage%20at%20the%20restaurant.%20Coupled%20with%20the%20sweet%20smells%20of%20their%20real%20counterparts%20that%20deck%20every%20nook%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365642%2Fbest-indian-dhabas-traditional-food-amrik-sukhdev-giani-puran-singh-chilika-end-dees-samaroh-ganga-kesar-rajinder%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earomas%20of%20delicacies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Banarasi%20%3Cem%3Epuri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20North-Indian%20snack)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebaingan%20bharta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20made%20with%20roasted%20eggplants)%20%E2%80%94%20they%20create%20a%20semblance%20of%20festive%20cheer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-9-1729604814.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%252C628%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20decor%20and%20interiors%20of%20Bungalow%20reflect%20Indian%20cultural%20sensibilities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-9-1729604814.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-9-1729604814.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebette